    <header class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
        Wardley Mapping Primer
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        Understand value streams and strategy with clear maps of users, needs, and components across evolution.
