        <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100">What is a Value Stream?</h2>
          <p>
            A value stream captures the flow of work and capabilities required to deliver value to a user. It spans
            from user needs to the underlying components that enable delivery.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100">What is a Wardley Map?</h2>
          <p>
            A Wardley Map visualizes a value chain (components linked by visibility to the user) against an
            <span class="font-semibold">evolution</span> axis (from genesis → custom → product → commodity). This helps teams reason
            about strategy, build vs. buy, and where to invest.
          </p>

          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            <li>Focus on the <span class="font-medium">user need</span> at the top.</li>
            <li>Identify components and their <span class="font-medium">dependencies</span>.</li>
            <li>Place components by their <span class="font-medium">evolution</span> maturity.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">Interactive sketch</h3>
